  "tips": [
    "The lake or pond of La Llebreta is located in the municipality of Vall de Boí, in the region of Alta Ribagorça, within the National Park of Aigüestortes y Lago de Sant Maurici\r\nCuriously, this lake is not of glacial origin like many others in the area, but was formed from a landslide of one of the mountains that caused a natural barrier in this valley.",
    "Waterfall of the Santo Nicolau river. We'll meet her right next to the path.",
    "Der Estany Llong liegt im Vall de Boí inmitten des Aigüestortes National Park and Estany de Sant Maurici auf knapp 2,000 Meter Höhe. Über den Gletschersee wacht der Portarró d'Espot."
